  - proc-call-lowering: Compiled call to rule go as ПП/В/О subroutine.
  - dispatch-default-residual-x-param: Passed residual-derived dir to go through X at line 52.
  - numeric-dispatch-residual-chain: Reused residual comparisons for numeric dispatch at line 47.
