  - dark-entry-layout: Pointed 3 branch(es) at an executable suffix through a proven dark-entry formal address (beyond the 104-cell window).
  - generated-setup-program: Generated optimized setup program for __coord_list_foxes_0, __coord_list_foxes_1, __coord_list_foxes_2, __coord_list_foxes_3, __coord_list_foxes_4, __coord_list_foxes_5, __coord_list_foxes_6, __coord_list_foxes_7, __coord_list_foxes_8.
  - setup-constant-synthesis: Built constant 100 by loaded exponent 2 and applied F 10^x (2 cells instead of direct 3).
  - setup-setup-coord-list-indirect-random-unique: Generated compact indirect setup for 9 unique coord_list item(s).
  - aggressive-post-layout-indirect-flow: Tried proven post-layout indirect-flow and dark-entry rewrites even though the primary layout already fit (60 vs 65 cells).

